MAP strategy:
Warning! Depending on the feed from saucer (2) this strategy might be unsafe! Shoot left ramp (1) 3 times and shoot right saucer (2). Do this over and over to collect nice modes like Jungle jackpot, Skill fire.
Jungle jackpot: A hurry up starts and you have to shoot saucer (2) as fast as possible. Highest value: 20M. This starts the 2-ball multiball. Objective: Shoot saucers (2 and 3) for jackpots. Both at the same time score a super jackpot of 40M.
Skill fire: Unlimited balls for 20 seconds. Objective: Launch balls at skill shot targets (4) OR left outlane (5), which is even better.
